sequenceDiagram
  autonumber

  box rgba(230, 240, 255, 0.35) Server (same Node process in dev)
    participant MW as middleware.ts
    participant RSC as Next.js RSC runtime
    participant Page as IssuesPage (Server Component)
    participant API as GET /api/issues (route.ts)
    participant Store as issues-store (globalThis)
  end

  participant BR as Browser
  participant Stats as IssueStatsClient (use client)
  participant Filters as IssueFilters (use client)

  rect rgb(245, 245, 245)
    Note over BR, Store: Phase A — First navigation: HTML produced on the server
    BR->>MW: GET /issues?status=…&sort=…
    alt No demo_session cookie
      MW-->>BR: 302 redirect to /
    else Cookie OK
      MW->>RSC: continue to route
      RSC->>Page: render IssuesPage (async)
      Page->>Page: await searchParams
      Page->>API: fetch(getBaseUrl + /api/issues?…), cache no-store
      API->>Store: listIssues() → copy/filter/sort
      Store-->>API: Issue[]
      API-->>Page: 200 { issues }
      Page->>Page: Build tree: IssueList → IssueCard (server) + client boundaries
      RSC-->>BR: HTML + RSC payload
    end
  end

  rect rgb(235, 250, 235)
    Note over BR, API: Phase B — After paint: JS loads, hydration + client fetches
    BR->>Stats: hydrate IssueStatsClient
    Stats->>API: fetch(/api/issues) from browser (React Query)
    API->>Store: listIssues() again
    Store-->>API: Issue[]
    API-->>Stats: 200 { issues } → count
    BR->>Filters: hydrate IssueFilters (router + URL)
  end
